casebody.data:
Nicholas David BURNETT, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Tracy Lynn AHOLA, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Derek Ahola, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157049
COA: 338618 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 23, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for immediate consideration is GRANTED. The motion for reconsideration of this Court's April 26, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
